sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Devenv as Dev Environment<br/>(devcontainer / Coder)
    participant LocalK8s as Local / Remote Cluster<br/>(Telepresence)
    participant Git as Git (GitHub / GitLab)
    participant CI as CI Pipeline
    participant CD as Argo CD
    participant Prod as Production Cluster

    Dev->>Devenv: Write code in standardised devcontainer
    Dev->>LocalK8s: Test against live cluster via Telepresence
    Dev->>Git: Raise Pull Request
    Git->>CI: Trigger CI pipeline
    CI->>CI: Lint, test, scan, build, sign
    CI->>Git: Update image tag in config repo
    CD->>Git: Detect manifest change
    CD->>Prod: Sync and deploy (canary → full rollout)
    Prod-->>Dev: Observability dashboards / alerts
